<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.3.7">
<l>oṉṟeṉap palaveṉa vaṟivarum vaṭiviṉu ṇiṉṟa</l>
<l>naṉṟeḻi ṉāraṇa ṉāṉmuka ṉaraṉeṉṉu mivarai</l>
<l>yoṉṟanum maṉattuvait tuḷḷinu mirupacai yaṟuttu</l>
<l>naṉṟeṉa nalañceyva tavaṉiṭai nammuṭai nāḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Remembering these called the very graceful Nāraṇaṉ, who stood in forms difficult</l>
<l>to know as one [and] as many, the four-faced one [and] Hara,</l>
<l>putting [them] in your minds as one, cutting off your great/two attachments,</l>
<l>is doing good that is good in him [during] our days.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
